This is the Hybrid version of apLCMS which is incorporating the knowledge of known metabolites and historically detected features on the same machinery to help detect and quantify lower-intensity peaks.
CAUTION: To use such knowledge, especially historical data, you must keep using (1) the same chromatography system (otherwise the retention time will not match), and (2) the same type of samples with similar extraction technique, such as human serum.
